job.title: Software Engineer
job.description:
I’m looking to hire ***Software Engineer/Electrical Engineer***  for MAQ Software to accelerate data-driven transformations and troubleshoot software initiatives that enable our customers to transform their industries.
Hiring candidates who have a Bachelor’s or a Master’s degree in Electrical Engineering, Electrical and Computer Engineering.
If you know anyone interested in a full-time, onsite engineering position for the Redmond, WA location, you can email at redmondjobs@maqsoftware.com or we would like to have a chat.
Freshers/Experienced/Graduates/Engineers/Post Graduates are welcome to apply.
